Class UserProfile

java.lang.Object
model.UserProfile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class UserProfile extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a user's profile, storing all their progress and statistics. This class is serializable to allow for saving and loading player data to/from disk. It tracks game stats, level progression, and experience points (XP).
